---
globs: *.prisma
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use kebab-case for file names (e.g. `api-chunk.prisma`)
- Use `@@map()` to map table names from camelCase to snake_case (e.g. `@@map("table_name")`)
- Use `@map()` to map fields names from camelCase to snake_case (e.g. `requestSchema Json? @map("request_schema")`)
